Guidelines, which Guidelines shall set out the expectations of directors, including basic duties and responsibilities with respect to
attendance at Board meetings and advance review of meeting materials;

The Board shall establish from time-to-time committees so as to assist
it in discharging its responsibilities and functions more effectively and so as to comply with all applicable rules and regulations relating
to the Corporation, and approve and periodically review their respective charters and limits of authority delegated to each committee;

